{"tid":723010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講下你屋企有咩無奈要買支那製產品","createTime":"2018-06-30T05:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T08:40:29.000Z","uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3528daf319c8d2c735869a66cd689c0579cbf80a","tid":723010,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"蔬菜<br />\n真係硬食，不過屋企都會盡量買外國水果<br />\n<br />\n肉類<br />\n屋企冇强求要活雞，唔洗比支那渣春袋。<br />\n巴西美國法國雞都好食。多數仲會間中買下丹麥同本地豬<br />\n<br />\n水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...<br />\n<br />\n低技術家庭電器<br />\n屋企共識係日本=歐美&gt;&gt;&gt;東南亞&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;支國，不過支國唔搞環保又平價勞工，啲大牌子都暫時仲係支國製<br />\n<br />\n手提電話<br />\n支那牌子一定唔買，不過apple同an機都係支那製(美國design cpu + 台韓廠)<br />\n都唔知支那有咩可以<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS<br />\n五毛+cctvb 新聞部 / 閪張東望+保皇狗<br />\n生癌死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdd37a41d3d5ea54a694597b89eec1838841593","tid":723010,"uid":15815,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"巴西果d衰過大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1174376fa0256b1c9d80fd56be3972e362fbee","tid":723010,"uid":47135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"蒜頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一包$5/6，本地有機要$22<br />\n生果同蔬菜都唔會買支那"},{"pid":"0d9aba4e0fb30903651e9a78bffd100b3905f52a","tid":723010,"uid":114064,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"你咪係大陸西囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學識打字先啦hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想扮香港人又唔識打正體字好易出事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee02a00c331eac8f59813223f19ab0627f4b69b0","tid":723010,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":